      "id": "PopularPost5619",
      "post_content": "Weird combo card that only got played in two kind of decks, self-milling decks with [Hermit Druid](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hermit Druid), and lock decks which used [Abundance](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Abundance) to reorder their deck at will, usually followed by [Sylvan Library](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sylvan Library) and [Gaea's Blessing](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gaea's Blessing) to constantly recycle [Time Walk](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Time Walk).",
